    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve absolutely gotta see this beauty! I\u2019ve taken such incredible care of this car that it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It's been garage-kept and pampered since day one\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust to be found. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, I promise you'll fall in love!",
      "price": 43900.0,
